Package space.sunqian.fs.di

Interface DIComponent

public interface DIComponent
Represents component of DIContainer, consisting of a type and a singleton instance of that type.

DIComponent is distinguished by type(), two DIComponent instances with same raw class but different generic type parameters are considered as two different components.
